{"tid":1153540,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基沙文加盟巴塞","createTime":"2019-05-13T16:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T17:22:48.000Z","uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"127903181f33548c3701a63d5b409650a2115c46","tid":1153540,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"5月13日訊 據塞爾電台消息，馬體會內部認為基沙文將會順利加盟巴塞，這周將就球員轉會事宜進行會談。<br />\n<br />\n  據悉，基沙文身邊人士均認為，格子將在今夏加盟巴塞。塞爾電台從馬體會球會方面獲悉，馬體會方面認為基沙文和巴塞已經達成了協議。<br />\n<br />\n  節目主播卡雷尼奧表示，格子非常接近加盟巴塞。本週他們將進行一次會談，馬體會方面希望基沙文如果已經與巴塞達成一致，就當面將自己的決定告知球會"},{"pid":"5a0fc28f39cc1222a906f8d64e540261f1dd45e4","tid":1153540,"uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"全世界加盟巴塞屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33344577e3fa7c784c5cfea9f3b5dd46e78c5197","tid":1153540,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"下年歐聯輪到俾馬體會反cup"},{"pid":"0c993a9b28c5391148c54032c0a639f17fd7a0a4","tid":1153540,"uid":83648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"世三對基沙文"},{"pid":"294feedf3e773e175c086ece75e00e422c1dc095","tid":1153540,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33344577e3fa7c784c5cfea9f3b5dd46e78c5197","tid":1153540,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"下年歐聯輪到俾馬體會反cup"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"畀C朗la<br />\n基沙文永遠的陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcb3662fd2c65662874bc3f1c9e561ac4b4f008","tid":1153540,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"294feedf3e773e175c086ece75e00e422c1dc095","tid":1153540,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33344577e3fa7c784c5cfea9f3b5dd46e78c5197","tid":1153540,"uid":52881,"like":0,"disli